         <h3 class="heading-c">
          Confronting bias
         </h3>
         <p>
          The Bias Response Support System is part of our commitment to address incidents of bias in ourÂ community.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-1-4">
         <figure class="icon-reverse">
