          </span>
         </figure>
         <h3 class="heading-c">
          Charting progress
         </h3>
         <p>
          Understanding the data and makeup of our community today helps us work toward a more inclusiveÂ campus.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-1-4">
         <figure class="icon-reverse">
          <span class="dashicons dashicons-clipboard">
          </span>
         </figure>
         <h3 class="heading-c">
          Planning an inclusiveÂ future
         </h3>
         <p>
          We are establishing best practices, creating foundational policies, and investing expert thought in improvingÂ inclusion.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-1-4">
